==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbacked
<hw>Un*backed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Never
mounted by a rider; unbroken.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unbacked</xex>
colts.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not supported or encouraged; not countenanced;
unaided.</def> <rj><au>Daniel.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbag</ent>⟦br⟧
